"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T12:59:50.000Z","msg":"唔好指指點點醫護手足啦<br />\n其他人唔罷<br />\n一味搬自己諗法、希望強加係哂醫護身上<br />\n講到其他人冇責任咁<br />\n之前講好左同醫護一齊擺<br />\n極多人走數都算<br />\n仲要屌番真係罷果班做得唔夠<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解醫護去唔盡<br />\n冇得show hand呀<br />\n因為你未罷工支持佢地<br />\n宜家得佢地罷緊工渣 </span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T13:59:16.000Z","msg":"得2,3日,點叫其他行業去做<br />\n人地9巴工會都決定緊"},{"pid":"f3081d4f819e18a92faccedb6cf7807a837bbae1","tid":1859981,"uid":40521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/OGJOBMw.png\" />"},{"pid":"d45ec46ea97ec91522d513e19dc5f40c9bc864a5","tid":1859981,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:35:24.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"6d498db44064e46c607b306e08c33fa3fe8422a8","tid":1859981,"uid":158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:35:57.000Z","msg":"大家幫手行多步宣傳下比你ig,fb,tg,Twitter 同身邊既朋友。<br />\n<br />\n聯署要求世衛主席辭職<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/united-nations-call-for-the-resignation-of-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-who-director-general\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Funited-nations-call-for-the-resignation-of-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-who-director-general&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KfDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=dc0c245a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/united-nations-call-for-the-resignation-of-tedros-adhanom-ghebreyesus-who-director-general</a><br />\n<br />\n美孚手足被爆頭要推上 twitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Domo96954201/status/1223987271344390144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDomo96954201%2Fstatus%2F1223987271344390144&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KfDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=a134aa6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDomo96954201%2Fstatus%2F1223987271344390144&h=df720d6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Domo96954201/status/1223987271344390144</a><br />\n<br />\n加入工會，組織力量<br />\n⚠️工會大全⚠️<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KfDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=cf859f38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"766df128cfb172635535f27fc52d6c5b9bae5513","tid":1859981,"uid":327590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:36:38.000Z","msg":"我想講，我地香港已經同中共撕裂，如果吾係無一個政府會咁想殺死呢代香港人，佢地淘汰呢班香港人，再係大陸入班人係好易容ge事！！！<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得醫護搵之峰幫手搵外國傾洽，每個國家都想有醫療人才加入，所以佢地呢班醫護好有價值，又可以幫佢地搵條後路，吾洗驚秋後算帳。<br />\n<br />\n例如：如果有日呢班罷工醫護用專才計劃離開香港時，外國可以加快完成手績給提供津貼等。<br />\n<br />\n原因有三：<br />\n1）吸引更多人罷工！醫護個個有技能，想走吾難，加上個香港依加變成咁，好多人都灰左，但如果外國肯優惠呢班罷工醫護比佢地更易移民，分分鐘會令藍絲想一起罷工，為自己搵多條出路<br />\n<br />\n2）有多一條路比醫護，保障佢地可以係無後顧之優做任何野，分分鐘可以包括埋5大訴求！！！<br />\n仲有吾識體諒的人都係藍絲，洗鬼理佢地咩意見？<br />\n<br />\n3）林鄭政府一下子比咁多人材流失，打破整個醫療體系，你估中共，香港人同世界會點睇林鄭？？香港引以為傲的醫療技術一直都係班中國人覺得最有價值的一樣野，你估佢地會點睇林鄭一個人攪到成pat屎出來？？要將個波傳番比林鄭"},{"pid":"0d1a6412358d9ca7b5fb5379eb05565f5dd1c23e","tid":1859981,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:37:00.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"ef4ac18abc7a0eeb0b1b73c92a9791c8fc338c2f","tid":1859981,"uid":33077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56a9619ec87935c4e30c6f0c597b62835bc51998","tid":1859981,"uid":104764,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T22:29:42.000Z","msg":"屌一味淨識推我哋罷<br />\n唔見其他行業有人響應？<br />\n<br />\n利申醫生  已罷"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:58:48.000Z","msg":"支持你<br />\n但你地呢行真係最直接有力<br />\n講真為自己條命著想<br />\n<br />\n政府見未好大鑊就推醫護做野先<br />\n到有人出事個時先做dd 野<br />\n踢一踢 郁一郁<br />\n經過sars 都唔識驚.唔講又要有醫護